<mxfile host="draw.io">
  <diagram name="store-and-forward" id="store-and-forward">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1600" dy="1000" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1500" pageHeight="720" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="bg" value="" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=none;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="0" y="0" width="1500" height="720" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="title" value="ストア&amp;フォワード (通信途絶耐性) のフロー" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=18;fontStyle=1" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="0" y="10" width="1500" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="laneN" value="" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e8f5e9;strokeColor=#82b366;verticalAlign=top" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="10" y="60" width="1480" height="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="labelN" value="通常時&#xa;(NW 正常)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=middle" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="30" y="90" width="120" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="devN" value="RS-232C 機器" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#555555" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="170" y="130" width="120" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="agN" value="Agent&#xa;(Rust / Go)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="410" y="130" width="150" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qN" value="Local Queue&#xa;(空 / 即消化)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="680" y="130" width="150" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="brN" value="tier1 Broker&#xa;(MQTT / Dapr)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="950" y="130" width="180" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="noteN" value="&#x2022; 電文は一度 SQLite (WAL) に書き、PUBACK 受信後に削除 (at-least-once)&#xa;&#x2022; Publish は MQTT QoS 1 (配信保証あり・重複許容)&#xa;&#x2022; tier1 側では idempotency key で重複排除&#xa;&#x2022; 定常負荷では Queue 滞留 = 0、遅延はミリ秒オーダー" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1160" y="90" width="320" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="eN1" value="RS-232C" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5" edge="1" parent="1" source="devN" target="agN">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="eN2" value="Enqueue" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5" edge="1" parent="1" source="agN" target="qN">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="eN3" value="Publish" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5" edge="1" parent="1" source="qN" target="brN">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="laneF" value="" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffebee;strokeColor=#c62828;verticalAlign=top" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="10" y="280" width="1480" height="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="labelF" value="断絶時&#xa;(NW / Broker 不達)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#c62828;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=middle" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="30" y="310" width="120" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="devF" value="RS-232C 機器" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#555555" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="170" y="350" width="120" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="agF" value="Agent&#xa;(Rust / Go)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#c62828" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="410" y="350" width="150" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qF" value="Local Queue&#xa;(滞留中 / WAL 拡大)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffcdd2;strokeColor=#c62828" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="680" y="350" width="150" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="brF" value="tier1 Broker&#xa;(到達不可)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#eeeeee;strokeColor=#999999;fontStyle=2" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="950" y="350" width="180" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xmark" value="✕" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=36;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#c62828" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="860" y="355" width="60" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="noteF" value="&#x2022; Publish 失敗時は指数バックオフで再試行 / Queue に滞留&#xa;&#x2022; Queue は FIFO・ディスクベース、電源断でも喪失しない&#xa;&#x2022; ディスク満時のポリシー: 最古電文破棄 / 重要度別優先 / 機器側バックプレッシャ (要業務判断)&#xa;&#x2022; TTL を超えた電文は old-data として別経路で記録" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1160" y="300" width="320" height="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="eF1" value="RS-232C" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5" edge="1" parent="1" source="devF" target="agF">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="eF2" value="Enqueue" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5" edge="1" parent="1" source="agF" target="qF">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="laneR" value="" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e3f2fd;strokeColor=#1565c0;verticalAlign=top" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="10" y="500" width="1480" height="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="labelR" value="復旧時&#xa;(NW 復旧後)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#1565c0;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=middle" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="30" y="530" width="120" height="150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="devR" value="RS-232C 機器" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#555555" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="170" y="580" width="120" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="agR" value="Agent&#xa;(Rust / Go)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#1565c0" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="410" y="580" width="150" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qR" value="Local Queue&#xa;(消化中 / FIFO)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#bbdefb;strokeColor=#1565c0" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="680" y="580" width="150" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="brR" value="tier1 Broker&#xa;(重複排除)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="950" y="580" width="180" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="noteR" value="&#x2022; 復旧検知は Publisher の ACK 回復で判定&#xa;&#x2022; Queue は FIFO 順で replay、token bucket でレート制御し broker 過負荷を防ぐ&#xa;&#x2022; 電文ヘッダに idempotency key (機器ID + timestamp + seq) を付与し tier1 で重複排除&#xa;&#x2022; リアルタイム電文と滞留電文は別パーティションで処理 (最新値優先の業務向け)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1160" y="520" width="320" height="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="eR1" value="RS-232C" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5" edge="1" parent="1" source="devR" target="agR">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="eR2" value="Enqueue" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5" edge="1" parent="1" source="agR" target="qR">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="eR3" value="Replay" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5" edge="1" parent="1" source="qR" target="brR">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
